A '''distortion field emitter''' was a device used to create a [[Distortion field/Legends|distortion field]], enabling those within the field to talk privately without concern that their conversation could be electronically bugged. The emitter could be positioned discretely as its appearance was like that of a rolled up pellet of [[Flimsiplast/Legends|flimsiplast]].

[[Kal Skirata]] used a distortion field emitter when discussing his anti-terror operation with [[Jaller Obrim]] at the [[Coruscant Security Force/Legends|Coruscant Security Force]] [[Coruscant Security Force Staff and Social Club|Staff and social club]].

